          <h3>November 2022 - December 2022</h3><br>
          <p>Pictoboards was a web app I made to recreate the feeling of Pictochat for the Nintendo DS on your computer. It's a front-end drawing based application using HTML canvas elements alongside a back-end server infrastructure. I wrote client javascript code using React and the server code was written in Node with Express. I also utilized Handlebars view engine to create template web pages for development. I wrote and retrieved information such as encrypted user account information to MongoDB using Mongoose.</p>
