          <h3>April 2022 - May 2022</h3><br>
          <p>Developed in a team of two, Little Guy Maker was an application I worked on inspired by the charm of various character creators. Little Guy Maker was developed using HTML canvas elements and javascript. I stylized mobile-friendly page design with Bulma and loaded application data from an external JSON file. Web components were used to standardize HTML elements. The most enjoyable aspect of this project was figuring out the mathematics to dynamically draw each body part from a single point.</p>
